Title: KitchenAid® NSF Certified Brushed Stainless Steel Mixing Bowl
Description: This brushed stainless steel mixing bowl is both handsome and durable. It is NSF certified, and fits models that start with KM.

Title: KitchenAid® Pasta Roller
Description: Roll homemade pasta dough into thick or thin sheets to create exquisite lasagna noodles or hand cut into fettuccini. Roller creates 6" wide sheets that feed perfectly into our various pasta cutters and ravioli maker.

Title: KitchenAid® Pasta Cutter
Description: Process a batch of dough into pasta with ease. The thick noodle cutter and angel hair pasta cutter included in this companion set cut thick pasta dough sheets into egg noodles and thin sheets into angel hair pasta.

Title: KitchenAid® Pouring Shield
Description: New one-piece pouring shield conveniently reduces splash-out when adding ingredients, fits only model KN15EX

Title: KitchenAid® Burnished Dough Hook
Description: Thoroughly and quickly mixes and kneads doughs for breads, rolls and coffee cakes. Fits models KSM5, KP50, KSMC50, KM25G0X

Title: KitchenAid® 11-Wire Whip
Description: This stainless steel whip's 11-wire design ensures that you'll get maximum volume in less time, for lighter, fluffier whipped cream, egg whites and cake batters. It fits Professional 5™ Plus Series models (starting with KV) and all 6-quart mixer models (starting with KP, KB, KD and KT).

Title: KitchenAid® Stainless Steel Mixing Bowl Polished
Description: This polished stainless steel 3-quart mixing bowl is both handsome and durable. It fits only models that start with KN15E1X.
